QuestData.Title: The Land Awakens
QuestData.Description:
The fiends in this cave were too much for me.
<Sharnax lets out a labored cough.>
I have seen what you can do.
I need you to slay these elementals before they reach their full potential. We cannot allow the Primalists to take control of Tyrhold!
QuestData.LogDescription: Defeat the Primordial Wrath and Primordial Hail in the Gelikyr Overlook.
QuestData.RewardText: Thank you for everything you have done for us, $c.
